<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM1.4">
<l>cuvariṟ purāṇaniṉ pērēḻutic cuṟavanaṟ koṭi(k)kaḷum turaṅkaṅkaḷuṅ</l>
<l>kavarip piṇākkaḷuṅ karuppuvilluṅ kāṭṭittan tēṉkaṇṭāy kāmatēvā</l>
<l>avaraip pirāyan toṭaṅkiyeṉṟu mātarit teḻuntaveṉ ṟaṭamulaikaṟ</l>
<l>ṟuvaraip pirāṉukkē caṅkaṟpittut toḻutuvait tēṉollai vitikkiṟṟiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Writing your names on the walls, O ancient one! See,</l>
<l>I have presented you with good banners with shark [emblems], horses,</l>
<l rend="indent">women with yak-tail fans, and a sugarcane-bow, O lord Kāma!</l>
<l>I have worshipped [you]Having intended my large breasts</l>
<l rend="indent">—which have always grown craving [Him] since childhood—</l>
<l>for the Lord of Dvārakā. Will you be able to intend [me for Him] promptly?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
